com.i2group.apollo.events.transport

Class EntitySupplantedEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.events.transport.Event
      • com.i2group.apollo.events.transport.EntitySupplantedEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEvent

    public final class EntitySupplantedEvent
extends Event
    The event that is created when one Entity is supplanted by another Entity as a result of a merge operation. Subsequent requests for a supplanted Entity retrieve the Entity that was merged into.
    Since:
    4.0
